Package arma

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllTests
    Executes all test cases.
    AllTestsArma
    Executes all test cases for Arma.
    AllTestsMat
    Executes all test cases for Mat.
    Arma
    Provides interfaces to non-member functions that are similar to the Armadillo C++ Algebra Library (Armadillo) by Conrad Sanderson et al., based on DenseMatrix64F from Peter Abeles' Efficient Java Matrix Library (EJML) Version 0.23 from 21.06.2013.
    Datum
    Provides pre-defined constants.
    Mat
    Provides a real-valued dense matrix with member functions and attributes that are similar to the Armadillo C++ Algebra Library (Armadillo) by Conrad Sanderson et al., based on DenseMatrix64F from Peter Abeles' Efficient Java Matrix Library (EJML) Version 0.23 from 21.06.2013.
    TestArmaElementWise
    Contains all test cases for parametrised interface tests of element-wise operations in Arma.
    TestArmaIndividual
    Contains all test cases for non-parametrised interface tests of operations in Arma.
    TestArmaMatrix
    Contains all test cases for parametrised interface tests of non-element-wise operations in Arma.
    TestData
    Provides several test matrices for parametrised interface tests as well as additional test parameters like the maximal allowed numeric tolerances.
    TestMatElementWise
    Contains all test cases for parametrised interface tests of element-wise operations in Mat.
    TestMatIndividual  
    TestMatMatrix
    Contains all test cases for parametrised interface tests of non-element-wise operations in Mat.
    TestUtil
    Provides methods for often repeated tasks within tests.
